g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解佢又要講大話<br />\n我係咪真係重蹈覆轍緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有人理下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我理解你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完你篇野我諗到幾樣野<br />\n<br />\n1. 拍拖真係會搵番同一類人 （我自己就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n2. 女人緣太好既男朋友真係令女朋友好易諗埋一二邊 因為佢係未拍拖之前就已經會同好多女仔朋友好close  所以唔會點理拍完拖之後既避忌  因為對佢黎講呢個已經係平常事 （唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 你有無同佢好認真咁傾過？搵一次機會同佢傾下 可以佢真係會避忌下 <br />\n<br />\n其實就算「佢地叫既」都可以拒絕嫁姐...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05927650dfddb952dae6e73ed0cd556c55b989d6","tid":33824,"uid":40310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:04:53.000Z","msg":"屌 真係好長"},{"pid":"463954feb28367ae3eeadc742d51582b0aee30ef","tid":33824,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"男不壞女不愛 如果佢一向對你好好你就唔中意佢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e3c05d52a35c66cbd7fa0108544c0c1cc33a1a","tid":33824,"uid":49874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:10:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd4f30debb82f9cc9e566609777cec98f4c476ca","tid":33824,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"因為佢仲未認真同妳拍拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主妳咁樣只會令自己辛苦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><del>有口話人無口